---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Privacy Policy - BetterCapture | Free Screen Recorder for Mac"
	description="BetterCapture's privacy policy. We collect zero data, have no tracking, no analytics, and no cloud uploads. Your recordings stay on your Mac."
	canonicalUrl="https://bettercapture.app/privacy-policy"
	robots="index, follow"
>
	<main class="pt-24 sm:pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-12 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
		<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-sm sm:prose-base">
			<h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 sm:mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-white/50 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

			<section class="space-y-6 text-white/70">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Overview</h2>
					<p>
						BetterCapture is a free, open-source screen recorder for macOS. Privacy is a core principle of this project. 
						BetterCapture does not collect, store, transmit, or process any personal data whatsoever.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Collection</h2>
					<p>BetterCapture collects <strong class="text-white">no data</strong>. Specifically:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-3">
						<li>No personal information is collected</li>
						<li>No usage analytics or telemetry</li>
						<li>No crash reports are sent</li>
						<li>No cookies or tracking technologies</li>
						<li>No third-party analytics services</li>
						<li>No account creation required</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

			<div>
				<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your Recordings</h2>
				<p>
					All screen recordings created with BetterCapture are stored locally on your Mac in the location you choose. 
					You have full control over what happens to your recordings after they are saved.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Network Activity</h2>
				<p>
					BetterCapture uses Sparkle for automatic updates. Sparkle periodically checks for new versions by 
					fetching update information from GitHub. This check does not include any personal information or 
					usage data. Update checks can be disabled in the app's preferences.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">macOS Permissions</h2>
				<p>
					BetterCapture requests the following macOS permissions to function:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-3">
					<li><strong class="text-white">Screen Recording</strong> - Required to capture your screen content</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Microphone</strong> - Optional, only if you choose to record microphone audio</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Camera</strong> - Optional, only if you choose to use the presenter overlay feature</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3">
					These permissions are managed entirely by macOS and can be revoked at any time in System Settings.
				</p>
			</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">This Website</h2>
					<p>
						The BetterCapture website (bettercapture.app) does not use cookies, analytics, or any tracking technologies. 
						No visitor data is collected or processed. The website is hosted on GitHub Pages.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Open Source Verification</h2>
					<p>
						BetterCapture is fully open source under the MIT license. You can verify all privacy claims by reviewing the 
						source code on <a href="https://github.com/jsattler/BetterCapture" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white underline hover:text-white/80">GitHub</a>.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
					<p>
						If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can open an issue on the 
						<a href="https://github.com/jsattler/BetterCapture/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white underline hover:text-white/80">GitHub repository</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</article>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
